snippet.title: Vacation Cafe Simulator | Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Cafe Simulator – a cozy game where you manage your own café on a tropical island! Craft delicious dishes to impress your guests, design your space, experiment with recipes, and grow your business to become a top vacation spot for tourists. Become a hospitality master and enjoy the relaxing island atmosphere. Subscribe to stay updated on development and see more about the game!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3196440/Vacation_Cafe_Simulator/
